{"tid":2154067,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張達明指延任「高招」 北京謀分化泛民 學者料抗爭派願協商","createTime":"2020-08-13T02:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T03:59:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7d00639b426f96e11ca719560c99777a36ecebbb","tid":2154067,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/5PRR2ZNBMSWHNDOKSDOL6MTH24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2F5PRR2ZNBMSWHNDOKSDOL6MTH24%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzkWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=86931abf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2F5PRR2ZNBMSWHNDOKSDOL6MTH24%2F&h=3cd1b7cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/5PRR2ZNBMSWHNDOKSDOL6MTH24/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n張達明指延任「高招」<br />\n北京謀分化泛民 學者料抗爭派願協商<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bS2fHAe9vm01BE5aaDcjIWK_4g0=/640x443/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RYRSQWGAOR2E2RWR5L4DVDVUBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbS2fHAe9vm01BE5aaDcjIWK_4g0%3D%2F640x443%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRYRSQWGAOR2E2RWR5L4DVDVUBM.jpg&h=047dceea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政治學者指團結是民主陣營最大力量。<br />\n<br />\n【禮崩樂壞】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會選舉押後一年，產生「真空期」問題，全國人大常委會終以《決定》方式宣佈現屆議員延任至下屆選舉為止。港大法律學院首席講師張達明批評有關做法等同重寫《基本法》，凸顯香港已走向中國特色「人大就係法律」，而過往絕少公開談政治的張達明，更形容中央讓包括DQ參選的四名民主派議員在內全體議員延任是「高招」，令民主派在去留問題上「鬼打鬼」。有政治學者相信民主派不會因延任問題分化，指即使強硬的本土抗爭派，也明白團結才是民主陣營最大力量。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會前日決定延續第六屆立法會「不少於一年」，直至第七屆立法會任期開始為止，更容許民主派議員在內全體議員延任，而目前民主派不同板塊就去留問題未有共識。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張達明又認為，人大雖在政治上解決問題，但今次決定也凸顯香港不再行普。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2VYiBBfO6-QVBRq33iVK0gPI-2A=/639x477/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VWOSLFIIIKH45FW7HIKIRWUYWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2VYiBBfO6-QVBRq33iVK0gPI-2A%3D%2F639x477%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVWOSLFIIIKH45FW7HIKIRWUYWY.jpg&h=77a1c5bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全國人大常委會前日決定現屆立法會議員可延任至下屆選舉為止。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「𠵱家係重新改寫基本法」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鄭松泰明言留低：總辭不着邊際<br />\n<br />\n至於人大決定的法律基礎是否穩妥，張直言：「到今時今日可以想像，中央點會容許小小地方法院，喺佢全面管治權下可以宣佈人大常委會做法違反《基本法》？」加上人大常委會有釋法這招撒手鐧，任何決定都不容挑戰。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所副行政總裁鍾劍華對「鬼打鬼」不太擔心，他指經歷了去年抗。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zV7kNZp-TribwYJZJccaV2tVL94=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZTGDNX3JPRNZKWD7BFF3BLRZ6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzV7kNZp-TribwYJZJccaV2tVL94%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZTGDNX3JPRNZKWD7BFF3BLRZ6M.jpg&h=54920ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張達明"},{"pid":"be9fb239a98e98143d7e66bc2820a0cce1599799","tid":2154067,"uid":238214,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:24:06.000Z","msg":"有咩咁高招.<br />\n泛民應該出聲明: 依1年我地照入立法會. 不過唔會去開會 杯葛議會<br />\n人工會捐出50% 比抗爭者做抗爭者基金"},{"pid":"724592069ee8e9eb7c3a5ba88f6a31beb7fab9d7","tid":2154067,"uid":98139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:25:24.000Z","msg":"其實KEEP住兄弟爬山就得 其他野理撚得佢"},{"pid":"33622ec2b35b5f1005536c192a2318f53504bf5c","tid":2154067,"uid":238214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:25:45.000Z","msg":"冇人講過入立法會 一定要開會+投票.<br />\n9 HEA 1年. 白呃1年政府人工. 再捐出去. D錢就買金條.<br />\n成立抗爭者基金"},{"pid":"7434bfad5de5bd369e557420635d85f34c59404a","tid":2154067,"uid":327462,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quot